  Given a preordered set <fr:tex>(A,  \le )</fr:tex>, the <fr:link
href="axt-003U.xml"
type="local"
addr="axt-003U">Alexandroff topology</fr:link> is
  the finest one among the topologies whose specialization preorders
  coincide with the order <fr:tex>\le</fr:tex>.
</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree
xmlns:fr="http://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-005P.xml"
