name="date-added">2024-01-13</fr:meta></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>
  Let <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> be a preordered set. The <fr:strong>upper topology</fr:strong> of <fr:tex>X</fr:tex> is the
  one generated by the subbasis consisting of complements of principal ideals.
</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
